#about.row
  %h3.center About
  %p.center
    :markdown
      Founded 2005. Monthly meetings, hackfests, & theatre. Frequent pub nights. We communicate via [mailing list](http://groups.google.com/group/boston-rubygroup) & [#boston.rb on IRC](http://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=boston.rb). Activity feeds are available via #{ link_to "Atom", "/events.atom" } or [Twitter](http://twitter.com/bostonrb). Thanks to our #{ link_to "sponsors", page_path(:sponsors) }. This Ruby web application is #{ link_to "open source", "http://github.com/bostonrb/bostonrb" }, available under the MIT license.

